INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('24110', '4', '2015-09-07 17:45:28', '2015-09-07 17:45:28', 'Mountain Paradise Hotel, in Arenal Volcano, Invites you to enjoy a real paradise, with the perfect balance between nature, service, simplicity and the fashionable.\nEnjoy the views of the volcano from the suspension bridges in the rainforest or while coasting through the air on a zip line excursion.\nThis remarkable project has a totally Costa Rican environment as its main strength, united to the highest standards in service. The hotel for 2016 will have 46 rooms, 36 premium suites, 3 master suites, 6 master deluxe and 1 honey room.\n\n<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong>Ameneties</strong></span>\n\n<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 0);\">Air Conditioning.Hot Water.Mini Refrigerator.Swimming Pool.Kids Pool.Cable TV.Spa.Coffee Service.Safe Deposit Box.</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 0);\">Laundry Service.Mini Gym.Conference Rooms.Currency Exchange.Private Parking.Internet Access.Wireless Internet</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 0);\">CD Player.Restaurant.Hair Dryer.Room Service.Telephone.Mini Bar.Bar.Handicap Accessible.Free Breakfast.Wet Bar.Volcano View.Gardens.Jacuzzi.</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong>Accommodations</strong></span>\n\n<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 0);\">Mini Refrigerator. Cable TV. Telephone. Hair Dryer. Safe Deposit Box. Jacuzzi .Air Conditioning.</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><strong>Premiun Suite</strong></span>\n<p class=\"dark-grey\" style=\"color: #6d6d6d;\"> <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 0);\">1 Bedroom. 1 King + 1 Queen.<span class=\"horiz-dot-list\" style=\"font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit;\">Volcano Views.</span> <span class=\"horiz-dot-list\" style=\"font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit;\">Alarm Clock</span> .<span class=\"horiz-dot-list\" style=\"font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit;\">Mini Bar.</span> <span class=\"horiz-dot-list\" style=\"