INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('23100', '1', '2015-04-23 04:42:09', '2015-04-23 04:42:09', '<h3><strong> <span style=\"color: #000000;\">Day 1</span></strong></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Welcome to Costa Rica! Private or shared air-conditioned    transportation from Int’l airport Juan Santamaria in San Jose to Hotel los Lagos</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<strong>2 nights’ accommodations at Hotel los lagos resort and spa in double standard room with daily breakfast included.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>A great Costa Rica vacation is waiting for you in a hot springs hotel featuring a really big natural outdoor area, which is both the largest piece of land among hotels in the zone and the very next to Arenal Volcano itself!, with an unique and wide range of services and facilities for the enjoyment of the volcano spectacular closest safe view, Costa Rica culture, people and cuisine, as well as the tropical rainforest flora &amp; fauna. All in one place at Los Lagos, Hotel Spa &amp; Resort!</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>The rooms are fully equipped featuring roomy private bath,hot water, hair driver ,air conditioning, cable tv,mini-fridge,safety box,electronic clocks  and of course ,a spectacular view of the arenal volcano.</strong>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Day 2</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Horseback Riding and Canopy Tours</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<strong>Join Los Lagos Hotel, Spa &amp; Resort horseback riding tour goes through the hotel’s hacienda and rainforest and then along the path that goes to Los Juncos Lake and passes on to the observatory where, on a clear day, you can appreciate the great view of the Arenal Volcano. Then we continue through one mile of primary tropical rainforest to Los Lirios Lake, giving you the chance for great bird watching and occasional wildlife sightings before riding back to the first lake.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>we stay for a while in the Arenal Volcano scenic point. You can see volcanic material descending from the conic crater and feel the power and beauty of the scenery formed simultaneously by the Arenal Volcano, this lake and the tropical rainforest.</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Afternoon canopy los cañones and The hot prings los lagos resort and spa and dinner</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<strong>The canopy route consists of 12 cables and 13 platforms, covering a full distance of 2.8 kilometers (1.7 miles), which makes this the longest and most memorable tour of its kind in the area. The cables\' lengths vary from 50 meters to 500 meters, with different heights and speeds.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>A Canopy Tour through the Costa Rican tropical rainforest gives you a chance to see wild life at its best. Keep your eyes open and you may catch a glimpse of the howler monkey, sloth, coati and many exotic birds.Once the tour is completed you will find yourself walking along a cobble-stoned path and crossing the crocodile and caiman farm, the frog farm and the butterfly garden. You can then relax in our hot or spring fresh pools, complete with water slides for no additional cost.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Don\'t forget that after an intense and active adventure day you can relax in the hotel’s natural hot springs.</strong>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Day 3</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Shared air-conditioned transportation from your hotel in Arenal area to hotel san bada Manuel Antonio national park &amp; beach</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<strong>3 nights’ accommodations at hotel san bada Manuel Antonio national park &amp; beach in standard room</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Hotel San Bada is located next to the World Famous Manuel Antonio National Park in Costa Rica, and close to Quepos Town</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>standard room are Beautifully decorated, air conditioned room with two full size beds, large bathroom with shower, hairdryer, iron and iron board (upon request), wardrobe, lcd 32″ cable tv, telephone, safety deposit box, alarm radio with clock, mini fridge (mini bar upon request) and furnished balcony. The room offers a view of the rainforest on the edge of Manuel Antonio National Park.</strong>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #008080;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Day 4</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Free Day, This day is yours to relax and enjoy Manuel Antonio beach</strong></span>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Day 5</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Sunset Sail and Snorkel Tour</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<strong>Come aboard as we cruise into the open sea, in search of spotted dolphins, migrating humpback whales, sea turtles and manta rays. While aboard our modern Catamaran boats, you will be captivated by the sight of frolicking dolphins in the boat’s wake, or the inimitable sound of a whale’s song. As we make our way down the coastline of Manuel Antonio National Park, the mysterious islands, jagged cliffs and unique rock formations will look almost close enough to reach out and touch. These are the nesting grounds and home for numerous species of marine birds, including pelicans, boobies and ibises, and that is before we’ve started snorkeling.</strong>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Day 6</strong></span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>shared air-conditioned transportation from manuel Antonio to Int’l Airport Juan Santamaria to catch your flight home</strong></span>\r\n\r\n[gravityform id=\"2\" title=\"true\" description=\"true\"]', '2 nights at Arenal, 3 nights at Manuel Antonio Beach (6 Days/ 5 Nights)', '<h5><span style=\"color: #008080;\"><strong>All of our packages are 100% customizable to fit your personal needs. Contact us today and let us be your personal travel agent! reservations@mmexperiencecr.com</strong></span></h5>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #008080;\"><strong> </strong></span></h6>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '2-nights-at-arenal-3-nights-at-manuel-antonio-beach-6-days-5-nights', '', '', '2015-08-31 20:41:04', '2015-08-31 20:41:04', '', '0', 'http://www.mmexperiencecr.com/product/paquete-de-6-noches-y-7-dias-fortuna-manuel-antonio-2/', '0', 'product', '', '0');
