untry or a specific area , direct contact with nature and biodiversity present .\" fa_icon=\"fa-leaf\"][vc_separator type=\"small\" position=\"center\" up=\"19\" down=\"24\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_separator type=\"small\" position=\"center\" up=\"19\" down=\"24\"][icon_text box_type=\"normal\" box_border=\"yes\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" fe_icon=\"icon_compass\" icon_type=\"normal\" icon_size=\"fa-3x\" icon_position=\"top\" title=\"Other Activities\" title_tag=\"h5\" icon_color=\"#393939\" title_color=\"#393939\" custom_icon_size=\"36\" icon_margin=\"0 0 5px 0\" fa_icon=\"fa-bicycle\" text=\"We offer a wide range of activities which can bring your adrenaline as well as your passion for nature to the fullest , you can read more in our reservation site\"][vc_separator type=\"small\" position=\"center\" up=\"19\" down=\"24\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type=\"row\" type=\"grid\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" content_menu_fe_icon=\"arrow_back\" text_align=\"center\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" padding_top=\"104\" padding_bottom=\"121\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>How we make the difference?</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>We are a Costa Rican family owned company created to show the world a pieces of this beautiful land.Rich of history, culture, delicious meals, biodiversity and the kindness of every persona who live in the country.</h3>\r\n<h3>Our company work with local and visitor adapting our services to the budget and preference of every customer, with the goal of deliver comfort and quick delivery</h3>\r\n<h3>Responsible and agile always pursuing a balance with sustainability.</h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type=\"row\" type=\"grid\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" content_menu_fe_icon=\"arrow_back\" text_align=\"center\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" padding_bottom=\"93\"][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"21722\" alignment=\"center\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\"][vc_separator type=\"transparent\" position=\"center\" up=\"34\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h5>Guayabo</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type=\"small\" position=\"center\" up=\"19\" down=\"24\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Costa Rica despite being a small country , is rich in history , with a number of places to visit that will give us an overview on how our indigenous people lived .</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type=\"transparent\" position=\"center\" up=\"20\" thickness=\"1\" down=\"0\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"21723\" alignment=\"center\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\"][vc_separator type=\"transparent\" position=\"center\" up=\"34\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h5>Mascara Boruca</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type=\"small\" position=\"center\" up=\"19\" down=\"24\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Handicrafts , architecture, cuisine, customs and music make us a country rich in culture, where visitors can not only see nature but also learn a little more about what is being Costa Rican .</h4>\r\n<div id=\"tw-target-text-container\" class=\"tw-ta-container tw-nfl\" style=\"color: #212121;\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<pre class=\"tw-data-text vk_txt tw-ta tw-text-small\"></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type=\"transparent\" position=\"center\" up=\"20\" thickness=\"1\" down=\"0\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"21724\" alignment=\"center\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_target=\"_self\" img_size=\"full\"][vc_separator type=\"transparent\" position=\"center\" up=\"34\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h5>Punta Islita</h5>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type=\"small\" position=\"center\" up=\"19\" down=\"24\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Unique and incredible scenery make Costa Rica a gem , where you can spend enjoying the best accompanied by the soothing touch that nature gives us holiday services .</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type=\"transparent\" position=\"ce