6600;\"><strong>Family standard </strong></span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">1king or 1x doublebeds. pull-out . air conditioning, cable TV, refrigerator, fan, safe, private bathroom with hot water service</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Casita</strong></span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">1king or 2x double beds. air conditioning, cable TV, refrigerator, fan, safe, private bathroom with hot water service.</span>\n\n[gravityform id=\"2\" title=\"true\" description=\"false\"]', 'Hotel Conchal', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '23239-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-13 21:44:15', '2015-09-13 21:44:15', '', '23239', 'http://www.mmexperiencecr.com/2015/07/09/23239-autosave-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
