INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('23453', '4', '2015-07-19 21:36:46', '2015-07-19 21:36:46', '<span style=\"color: #333300;\">Croc’s Hotel is right on the Pacific Ocean with Three Restaurants, a Disco, a Las Vegas style Casino, and Four Star Pool.Breakfast at the luxury Hotel in Jaco, Costa Rica - Crocs HotelStrategically situated against the backdrop of the breathtaking Pacific Ocean and flanked by the Costa Rican Rain Forest and the charming town of Jaco, Croc’s Casino Resort soars a luxurious 17 story building with 152 stunning hotel rooms.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">There’s nothing like Croc’s Hotel in Costa Rica. Our expansive Las Vegas Style gaming facility was designed to play in a tropical setting with ocean views, exciting action all surrounded in natural architecture. Whether you prefer the newest array of slots or table games you’ll find a full selection of your favorite games.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">Owners as well as hotel guests will enjoy the largest collection of on-site amenities in Costa Rica. Gracious service at every turn, lounges for anytime cocktails, gourmet, casual and quick service restaurants, nightly entertainment, a vibrant disco, relaxing full service spa and beauty salon, gym and retail shop among others</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Amenities</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">Convention Center. Spa and beauty salon .disco. Three Restaurants . Coffee Shop. Three Fun Bars. Las Vegas Style Casino. Five-Star Pool &amp; Poolside Bar</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong> </strong><strong>Accommodations</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">Luxurious bedding with ultra-premium mattress &amp; Duvet ,Exquisite bathroom amenities. Safety Deposit Box. Alarm Clock with iPod dock.Makeup mirror. Cable TV. Slippers. Evening turndown service. Fridge.24 hr. Room Service. Bathrobes.Rollaway &amp; Cribs available upon request.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Deluxe Mountain View Room - without balcony</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">2queen bed o 1 king. shower, Mini Refrigerator .safe deposit box</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Deluxe Mountain View Room  - with balcony</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">2 queen bed o 1 king. shower, Mini Refrigerator .safe deposit box</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Deluxe Ocean View Room - without balcony</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">2 queen bed o 1 king. Mini Refrigerator .safe deposit box. bathtub.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong> </strong><strong>Deluxe Ocean View Room  - with balcony</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">2 queen bed o 1 king.  Mini Refrigerator .safe deposit box .bathtub.</span>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Junior Suite Mountain View - without balcony  </strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">2 queen bed o 1 king. shower, Mini Refrigerator .safe deposit box</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Junior Suite Mountain View - with balcony</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">2 queen bed o 1 king. shower, Mini Refrigerator .safe deposit box</span>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Junior Suite Ocean View - without balcony</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">2 queen bed o 1 king.  Mini Refrigerator .safe deposit box .bathtub.</span>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Junior Suite Ocean View with Balcony</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">2 queen bed o 1 king.  Mini Refrigerator .safe deposit box .bathtub.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong> </strong><strong>Deluxe Terrace Ocean View (400 sqf.)</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">2 queen bed o 1 king.  Mini Refr