INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('23759', '4', '2015-08-03 00:13:41', '2015-08-03 00:13:41', 'El hotel está situado a sólo 5 minutos del Parque Nacional Tortuguero, y cerca del \"canal\" principal que enfrenta el pueblo de Tortuguero. Rodeado por una red de canales escénicos. Esta es considerada una de las regiones más exóticas del mundo, caracterizados por su rica flora y fauna.\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Amenities</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nRestaurante.WIFI. piscina.agua caliente .MiniRefrigerador.piscina para Niños.Spa.caja fuerte .Jacuzzi.vista al jardín .ventilador .bar\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Accommodations</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAgua caliente .caja  fuerte. ventilador\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Paquete 2 Días / 1 noche </strong>\r\n\r\nVista al jardín  Vistas al bosque transporte Porche Planta, traslados en barco y salir, todas las comidas y excursiones incluidas.\r\n\r\nCapacidad 3 en 1 dormitorio. 1 rey (o) 3 individual (o) 2 Doble\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Paquete 3 Días / 2 Noches</strong>\r\n\r\nVista al jardín . Vista al bosque  transporte terrestre, traslados en barco dentro y fuera, todas las comidas y excursiones incluidas.\r\n\r\nCapacidad 3 en 1 dormitorio. 1 rey (o) 3 individual (o) 2 Doble\r\n\r\n[gravityform id=\"1\" title=\"true\" description=\"false\"]', 'Hotel Pachira Lodge', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'hotel-pachira-lodge', '', '', '2015-08-03 00:19:14', '2015-08-03 00:19:14', '', '0', 'http://www.mmexperiencecr.com/product/hotel-pachira-lodge-2/', '0', 'product', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('23760', '4', '2015-08-03 00:38:17', '2015-08-03 00:38:17', 'Turtle Beach Lodge in Tortuguero National Park,  is a secluded hotel resort spanning 175 acres. It encompasses miles of jungle trails, a meandering private canal and a half mile of isolated beach on the Caribbean Sea.  the  lodge provides highly trained staff and guides who ease you into an extraordinary jungle experience. Tortuguero has incredible biological variety due to the existence of eleven different habitats, including rainforest, swamps, beaches and lagoons. The beaches are a key nesting ground for endangered sea turtles, including Hawksbill, Loggerheads, Green and Leatherbacks. Manatees, caiman and crocodiles live in the canals and the jungle is home to endangered jaguars, three species of monkeys (spider, howler, and white-faced Capuchin) and three-toed sloths. Basilisk lizards and tree frogs inhabit the area, along with 375 species of birds. There are more than 400 species of trees and approximately 2,200 species of plants.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 128);\"><strong>Amenities</strong></span>\r\n\r\nRestaurant . Swimming Pool . Safe Deposit Box .Fan.Hiking Trails.Restaurant .Hammocks .Bar .Gardens\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 128);\"><strong>Accommodations</strong></span>\r\n\r\nHot Water.fan. private baths\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 128);\"><strong>Package 2 Days/1 Night</strong></span>\r\n\r\n2 Double bed (or) 2 Double + 1 Single (or) 1 Double.\r\n\r\nGardens Views. Porch Sleeps 4 in 1 Bedroom\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 128);\"><strong>Package 3 Days/2 Nights</strong></span>\r\n\r\n2 Doublebed (or) 2 Double + 1 Single (or) 1 Double.Gardens Views. Sleeps 4 in 1 Bedroom\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 128);\"><strong>Package 4 Days/3 Nights </strong></span>\r\n\r\n2 Double (or) 2 Double + 1 Single (or) 1 Double.Gardens Views .Porch .Sleeps 4 in 1 Bedroom\r\n\r\n[gravityform id=\"2\" title=\"true\" description=\"false\"]', 'Hotel Turtle Beach Lodge', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'hotel-turtle-beach-lodge', '', '', '2015-08-05 20:37:48', '2015-08-05 20:37:48', '', '0', 'http://www.mmexperiencecr.com/?post_type=product&#038;p=23760', '0', 'product', '', '0');
