s Views Jacuzzi</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">Standard Room</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">1 Bedroom. 1 Queen + 1 Double.</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">Volcano Views Gardens Views Wheelchair Accessible</span>\n<p class=\"large bold\" style=\"font-weight: 900; color: #3e220f;\"><strong>[gravityform id=\"2\" title=\"true\" description=\"true\"]</strong></p>', 'Hotel volcano inn', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '23059-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-02 21:26:06', '2015-09-02 21:26:06', '', '23059', 'http://www.mmexperiencecr.com/2015/09/02/23059-autosave-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
