ensilla + 2 Queen.Cocina. Jardines Vistas .Mini Nevera</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Junior Suite</strong></span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">2 camas Queen.vista al jardin. Mini Refrigerator. Wheelchair Accessible</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Ocean Beach Front Room</strong></span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">1 King + 2 Double.Beachfront Views. Mini Refrigerator</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Standard Jungle Room</strong></span>\n\n1 Queen. Gardens Views\n\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Standard Room</strong></span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">Sleeps 3 in 1 Bedroom. 1 Queen + 1 Double.Gardens Views</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Superior Room</strong></span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">1 King.Gardens Views. Mini Refrigerator .Wheelchair Accessible</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Beach Front Apartment</strong></span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">1 King + 1 Queen.Beachfront Views .Mini Refrigerator</span>\n\n<strong> </strong>[gravityform id=\"1\" title=\"true\" description=\"true\"]', 'Hotel cariblue', '<p><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '23915-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-21 01:49:30', '2015-09-21 01:49:30', '', '23915', 'http://www.mmexperiencecr.com/2015/09/21/23915-autosave-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES('24293', '4', '2015-09-21 02:49:39', '2015-09-21 02:49:39', '<span style=\"color: #333300;\">Apartamentos Agapi is a 10-minute walk from the center of Puerto Viejo de Limón. Set along the Caribbean coast,</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">Agapi is a Greek word that expresses a love for the things that one cares about. This hotel, run by a Greek and Costa Rican couple, is an expression of this sort of love. Meticulously maintained and comfortably designed, Apartamentos Agapi is a great place to stay at while visiting Puerto Viejo. It’s homey, on the beach, and just a short walk from the center of town.  </span>\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\"> </span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Amenities</strong></span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">Laundry Service,Wireless Internet,Private Parking,Cable TV,Breakfast Available,Hot Water,Internet Access,</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">Kitchen,Mini Bar,Free Breakfast,Balcony,Ocean View,Fan,Hammocks,Safe Deposit Box,Currency Exchange</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">Air Conditioning,Swimming Pool,Kids Pool.</span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Accommodations</strong></span>\n\n<span style=\"color: #333300;\">Mini Refrigerator ,Wireless Internet, Cable TV, Fan, Hot Water ,Air Conditioning, Balcony.</span>\n<p class=\"large bold\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">Standard Room</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"dark-grey\"><span style=\"color: #333300;\"> 1 Bedroom. 1 Doublebed + 2 Single.</span></p>\n<strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">Suite Apartment</span></strong>\n<p class=\"dark-grey\"><span style=\"color: #333300;\">1 Bedroom. 1 Double bed + 2 Single.</span></p>\n<p class=\"large bold\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Apartment</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"dark-grey\"><span style=\"color: #333300;\"> 1 Bedroom. 1 Double bed.</span></p>\n&nbsp;\n\n[gravityform id=\"2\" title=\"true\" description=\"true\"]', 'Agapi Apartments', '<p><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '23026-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-21 02:49:39', '2015-09-21 02:49:39', '', '23026', 'http://www.mmexperiencecr.com/2015/09/21/23026-autosave-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
